com.qualcomm.hardware.modernrobotics.comm

Class RobotUsbDevicePretendModernRobotics

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.qualcomm.hardware.modernrobotics.comm.RobotUsbDevicePretendModernRobotics

  • public class RobotUsbDevicePretendModernRobotics
extends java.lang.Object
    This class implements a dummy RobotUsbDevice that will apparently successfully do reads and writes but doesn't actually do anything.
